name: Managed Service for MySQL — Host overview

targets.query: alias(series_max("systag", "cpu.*"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", host="{{host}}", resource_id="{{cluster}}", node="*", resource_type="cluster", systag="*"}), "{{systag}}")
alias(series_max("systag", trunc("mem.*"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", host="{{host}}", resource_id="{{cluster}}", resource_type="cluster", node="*", systag!="-"})), "{{systag}}")

top_max(10, alias(series_max("filetype", "mysql.fileio.write_bytes"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", resource_type="cluster", resource_id="{{cluster}}", host="{{host}}"}), "{{filetype}}"))

top_max(10, alias(series_max("filetype", "mysql.fileio.read_bytes"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", resource_type="cluster", resource_id="{{cluster}}", host="{{host}}"}), "{{filetype}}"))

top_max(10, alias(series_max("filetype", "mysql.fileio.writes"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", resource_type="cluster", resource_id="{{cluster}}", host="{{host}}"}), "{{filetype}}"))
top_max(10, alias(series_max("filetype", "mysql.fileio.reads"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", resource_type="cluster", resource_id="{{cluster}}", host="{{host}}"}), "{{filetype}}"))

top_max(10, alias(series_max("handler", "mysql.handler"{folderId="{{folderId}}", service="managed-mysql", resource_type="cluster", resource_id="{{cluster}}", host="{{host}}"}), "Handler_{{handler}}"))
